    "rationale": "Despite all 13 credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5, the assessment package is accepted for submission to regulatory review as a complete documentation of credibility gaps. The decision reflects acceptance of the evidence package as a structured gap analysis, not acceptance of the model for clinical use. No applicability constraints or operating envelope have been specified in the ContextOfUse, leaving the valid range of model use formally unspecified.",
